CustomField.description: Controls the pixel width for Milestone dropdown on Timecard Entry UI. Please specify a whole number for this value, as this will directly go into width. For ex a value 300 will set the dropdown width to 300px. Value specified for this config will override the default 80 pixel width of the dropdown.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Controls the pixel width for Milestone dropdown on Timecard Entry UI. Please specify a whole number for this value, as this will directly go into width.
CustomField.label: Width_px_for_milestone_drop_down
